OL,3,CKirkstone Pass to reopen on Friday
OL,4,Cafter landslip repairs
OL,6,FDrivers have seen long diversions
OL,7,Fsince a landslip undermined part of an
OL,8,Fimportant Lake District road in
OL,9,FNovember 2025.
OL,11,FAt the time, Westmorland and Furness
OL,12,FCouncil's Highways team warned it
OL,13,Fwould not be a quick fix but promised
OL,14,Fto repair the road in time for the
OL,15,Fbusy summer holidays.
OL,17,FNow it has announced the A592
OL,18,FKirkstone Pass will reopen on Friday
OL,19,FJuly 17.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
