OL,3,CKirkstone Pass to reopen on Friday
OL,4,Cafter landslip repairs
OL,6,FAn emergency road closure was put in
OL,7,Fplace when heavy rainfall caused a
OL,8,Flandslide that partly undermined the
OL,9,Fcarriageway at High Kingate, halfway
OL,10,Fbetween Troutbeck and the Kirkstone
OL,11,FInn, just before the start of the
OL,12,FKirkstone Pass itself.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
